04:44.600 --> 04:46.780
Lumayan.

04:46.830 --> 04:48.110
Namun, kamu jangan pergi sendiri.

04:48.130 --> 04:49.130
Nanti kamu tersesat lagi,

04:49.190 --> 04:50.290
